    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Lumbrineris luciliae sp. nov. Paratype (ECOSUR 0129) A, anterior end, dorsal view; B, parapodium 3, frontal view; C, parapodium 13, frontal view; D, parapodium 77, frontal view; E, composite multidentate hooded hook, from parapodium 3; F, simple multidentate hooded hook from parapodium 77; G, acicula from parapodium 86; H, maxillae III and IV, dorsal view. Scale bars: A, 1.0 mm; B, C, D, H 0.1 mm; E, F, 0.025 mm; G, 0.01 mm." ;
